'''初精'''是指[[青春期|青春期]]男性的[[睪丸|睪丸]]初次分泌[[精子|精子]]<ref name="a">''Adolescence and Emerging Adulthood: A Cultural Approach'', Jeffrey Jensen Arnett,  N.J.: Prentice-Hall, 3rd edition, 2006. ISBN 9780131950719</ref>，或是第一次[[射精|射精]]，和女性的[[初潮|初潮]]類似，都是生殖器官發育中會出現的情形<ref>''Adolescence'', E. Atwater, Englewood Cliffs, N.J.: Prentice-Hall, 3rd edition, 1992. ISBN 9780130074690</ref><ref name="c">{{Cite journal|title=The Onset of Sperm Production in Pubertal Boys: Relationship to Gonadotropin Excretion|url=http://archpedi.jamanetwork.com/article.aspx?doi=10.1001/archpedi.1989.02150140080024|last=Kuhn|first=Howard E.|date=1989-02-01|journal=American Journal of Diseases of Children|issue=2|doi=10.1001/archpedi.1989.02150140080024|volume=143|pages=190|language=en|issn=0002-922X|access-date=2022-06-06|archive-date=2020-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200404000700/https://jamanetwork.com/journals/jamapediatrics/article-abstract/514473}}</ref>。青春期男性對於初精會有不同的反應，從懼怕到興奮甚至欣慰都有<ref name="a" />。

初精表示男性將要進入[[性成熟|性成熟]]的階段，發生在第二性徵正要開始發育的時候<ref name="d">{{Cite journal|title=Onset of the Release of Spermatozia (Supermarche) in Boys in Relation to Age, Testicular Growth, Pubic Hair, and Height*|url=https://academic.oup.com/jcem/article-lookup/doi/10.1210/jcem-62-3-532|last=Nielsen|first=C. Thøger|last2=Skakkebæk|first2=Niels E.|date=1986-03|journal=The Journal of Clinical Endocrinology & Metabolism|issue=3|doi=10.1210/jcem-62-3-532|volume=62|pages=532–535|language=en|issn=0021-972X|last3=Richardson|first3=David W.|last4=Darling|first4=Janet A. B.|last5=Hunter|first5=William M.|last6=Jørgensen|first6=Merete|last7=Nielsen|first7=Aage|last8=Ingerslev|first8=Olaf|last9=Keiding|first9=Niels|access-date=2021-06-19|archive-date=2020-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200404000715/https://academic.oup.com/jcem/article-abstract/62/3/532/2674705?redirectedFrom=fulltext}}</ref>。初精的年齡不容易判斷，不過研究者試著在不同的族群中採集男孩的過夜尿液，檢驗當中是否有[[精子|精子]]<ref name="c" />。根據不同的研究資料，初精約在9歲到13歲之間<ref name="d" />。

在一項研究中，男孩被問到第一次射精的情況。最常見的是通過夜間[[遺精|遺精]]發生的，相當多的男孩通過[[自慰|自慰]]經歷了初精。比較少見的是，第一次射精發生在與異性進行[[性交|性交]]時。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Physical Development in Boys: What to Expect|url=https://www.healthychildren.org/English/ages-stages/gradeschool/puberty/Pages/Physical-Development-Boys-What-to-Expect.aspx|accessdate=2021-04-18|work=HealthyChildren.org|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511120452/https://www.healthychildren.org/English/ages-stages/gradeschool/puberty/Pages/Physical-Development-Boys-What-to-Expect.aspx}}</ref>

==概要==

它是男孩性成熟过程中一个重要的过程，对应于女孩的[[初潮|初潮]]。同时也可以证明已经产生了精液，并且导致射精的性功能发育过程没有异常，并且能够与达到月经期的女孩一起获得了生育能力。这意味着他们从孩子到成年的身体过程中已经成长了一步。

